---
title: Spicy Coconut Turkey Curry Soup with Tomato, Carrot, Zucchini, Scallions & Cilantro
description: Vibrant Indian flavors take center stage in this lush, savory-sweet, and spicy curry soup. Here, aromatic scallion, garam masala, curry powder, garlic, carrot, and tomato are cooked together until fragrant. Next, ground turkey is browned, then zucchini, cilantro, and chili flakes are added to create more layers of flavor—all simmered in coconut milk and savory vegetable stock in one pot. To finish, scallion greens and more cilantro are sprinkled over the top for pops of color and herbaceous flavor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651c1e88f8c6c435c24a9687-6cc0eb6e.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/651c1e88f8c6c435c24a9687.pdf
cuisine: Asian
